      "id": "ev_out",
      "x": 818,
      "y": 480,
      "width": 446,
      "height": 110,
      "text": "  step \"extract-entries\"   gpt-5.1   done -> cached\n  step \"score-fit\"          gpt-4.1   done -> cached\n  step \"tailor-sections\"    gpt-4o    running...\n  step \"persist\"            Postgres  pending\n  -> resumes mid-run, never re-bills a done step",
      "originalText": "  step \"extract-entries\"   gpt-5.1   done -> cached\n  step \"score-fit\"          gpt-4.1   done -> cached\n  step \"tailor-sections\"    gpt-4o    running...\n  step \"persist\"            Postgres  pending\n  -> resumes mid-run, never re-bills a done step",
